21. QUICK STATIC IP SETUP
-------------------------------------------------

sudo ip link set eth0 up

sudo ip addr add 192.168.1.100/24 dev eth0

sudo ip route add default via 192.168.1.1

echo "nameserver 8.8.8.8" | sudo tee /etc/resolv.conf

-------------------------------------------------
22. QUICK DHCP SETUP
-------------------------------------------------

sudo ip link set eth0 up

sudo dhclient eth0

Verify:
ip a
ip route
cat /etc/resolv.conf

-------------------------------------------------
23. NETWORK TROUBLESHOOTING FLOW
-------------------------------------------------

1. ip link
   → Is interface UP?

2. ip a
   → Does it have an IP?

3. ip route
   → Is there a default gateway?

4. ping <gateway>
   → Local network reachable?

5. ping 8.8.8.8
   → Internet reachable?

6. ping google.com
   → DNS working?

7. cat /etc/resolv.conf
   → Correct DNS server?

8. ss -tulnp
   → Required service listening?

9. traceroute <host>
   → Where is traffic failing?
